Package projectone.demo.model

Class Inventory

java.lang.Object
projectone.demo.model.Inventory
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Entity(name="Inventory") public class Inventory extends Object implements Serializable
Entity representation of the inventory table used to store inventory items details. This class is annotated with JPA annotations to map it to the database table "inventory". It uses Lombok annotations to automatically generate getters, setters, and constructors.

      The unit of measurement for the inventory item quantity. This field cannot be null.

    • lowThreshold

      private Integer lowThreshold
      The low stock threshold. When inventory quantity falls below this value, it indicates that the item is running low. This field cannot be null.

    • orderDate

      private LocalDate orderDate
      The date on which the last order was made for this inventory item. This field helps in tracking when the item was last ordered. This field cannot be null.
